data.description: COUNTRY BLISS! This 4 bed 2.5 bath home sits on a sprawling 16 acres! Recent updates to the home give it a farmhouse feel. The property includes a pasture for animals, ideal garden space, chicken coop, wooded section with trails for walking or ATV riding, and a hefty deer blind in the back for prime hunting. 2 outbuildings offer space for animals or a workshop, one having a working bathroom. The property has 3 pressurized artesian wells, a new furnace in the upstairs attic that can be connected to AC, conduit electrical throughout, apple and pear trees and many other amazing features! Seller offering $5,000 flooring credit with acceptable offer.
